===English===

==Etymology==
Anthony (Tony) Blair, Leader of the British [[Labour party]], and UK [[prime minister]] at the turn of the twentyfirst century.

==Adjective==
#A term used to describe the [[populist]] or [[right wing]] policies introduced by the UK government from 1997-, which were largely seen to a move away from tradional Labour values.
#A term used to describe a supporter of Tony Blair

